description: A sustainability comparison tool titled 'Agder 2050: Our Choice' showing the Agder region in different future scenarios (2050). Features satellite/standard map toggle, comparison modes (Today vs. Sustainable 2050 vs. Non-sustainable 2050), image slider comparison for Tangen VGS future visualization, flood/drought/fire risk zones, sustainability tips section, news section, and an AI 'Climate Expert' chatbot.
